vironment 有so，上堂用普通話多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93d0239224af7db570795e02f736a32b08a7ec0","tid":2022676,"uid":147420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ecb0fc2c52fa8dd7d486c2b9da77b4e7995102","tid":2022676,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"點解鍾意marketing 點睇呢個行業前景 點睇digital marketing"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得近半年搞到好多行業受挫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人都變左上網買嘢，所以呢個e-commerce嘅trend增加左對digital marketing嘅需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（Digital mkt同IT都好有關，我自己都學緊少少coding）<br />\n<br />\n啱啱八掛聽到Alex個consultation talk話我哋program fresh grad個average salary係above $17,000，不過s.d. 好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e9f21dddd7d9379442ffb02adcddfc528a0f56","tid":2022676,"uid":147420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"Btw 星期三同星期四都有zoom consultation sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ae5c705afa4a276ac4d57be9b7f96760930585","tid":2022676,"uid":147420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"07ab200cee64fb2b58b4680bdc178f9f1f75fe0b","tid":2022676,"uid":120064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"marketing係讀啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfc16dd828bfc9146af03a16e1c9ca45eb0088e","tid":2022676,"uid":147420,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"07ab200cee64fb2b58b4680bdc178f9f1f75fe0b","tid":2022676,"uid":120064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"marketing係讀啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"主要學Analytics同Design Thinking (Problem solving) 。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Analytics就最實用，透過用唔同分析結果的工具，做pj個陣可以用最短時間得到詳盡既分析結果，省番好多時間! 好似我上個sem上Market Research咁，用SPSS就可以即刻知道問卷result 既trend, interviewee performance等等。學左呢d Analytics tools又可以整靚份CV，之後又可以apply係intern 啲 jobs到添，無敵!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDesign thinking方面，要謹記以人為本的大原則！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />堂上會有好多case study，比我地了解唔同知名品牌在市場上點樣用設計思維技巧設計創意嘅產品和服務，喺競爭激烈嘅市場下脫穎而出，培養創新思維，啟發我地既靈感小宇宙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日要晏啲先再覆到大家</span> </span>"},{"pid":"5a5efc738db9031dd2dae1e3e6b3f3319206f379","tid":2022676,"uid":305302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"Analytic 使唔使計statistic ? 同埋有冇推薦嘅cb course ? <br />\n利申year 1 city mkt"},{"pid":"46264a35e8ae8b6471905e4e9b578b3f3fa7626d","tid":2022676,"uid":147420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5efc738db9031dd2dae1e3e6b3f3319206f379","tid":2022676,"uid":305302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"Analytic 使唔使計statistic ? 同埋有冇推薦嘅cb course ? <br />\n利申year 1 city mkt"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"Analytics 係涉及少少statistic嘅野，但唔會好似DSE啲數學咁要瘋狂計數。我地多數都會用software (e.g. SPSS, Excel) 去分析數據同資料。只要識用啲software就掂唒，所以數理底唔太勁既都唔洗緊張。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推薦嘅CB course，CB2021 Big data同LW2903 Business and Law都係靚grade科，可以揀。<br />\n聽人講CB2021 Big data，group project同presentation都係按個人比分，唔洗驚比free-rider拖累。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要學嘅technique野唔會話太深奧，商科人都應付到。<br />\n<br />\nLW2903 Business Law主要以case study and analysis為主，只要明白啲theory同點apply就ok。而且啲case都好貼近生活，都幾有趣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果major唔係mkt，普通話又勁嘅話， CB3042 China Business Environment 都係好選擇!!堂上用普通話教授，敎啲野都易明，唔洗死背，上堂幾輕鬆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但記得要多啲答問題，participation佔幾重!"},{"pid":"9e6cb3bca923742cacbda5299b4ed2ffdf922bbd","tid":2022676,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"Not 有個韓仔啊sir好好人<br />\nElective最易讀最網好grade一定係is dept既科"},{"pid":"04d9a3c13cedfa3e3cfb9446486b6f7976b7b0e9","tid":2022676,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e6cb3bca923742cacbda5299b4ed2ffdf922bbd","tid":2022676,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"Not 有個韓仔啊sir好好人<br />\nElective最易讀最網好grade一定係is dept既科"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"Mkt"},{"pid":"cd697c6a06fbb26acfee9de007a2967852a7dca8","tid":2022676,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mkt 有個韓仔啊sir好好人<br />\nElective最易讀最網好grade一定係is dept既科</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c7b6239e5c42363cef51020c6a136f7fdcc7e54","tid":2022676,"uid":20431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8aa07d768bf14eef6e0462e272379aecc8fbbd0","tid":2022676,"uid":56498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"做緊Marketing的shitty畢業生路過<br />\n發現有d人問嘅問題真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. City作為一間2nd tier的學校，個朵比唔上三大是常識吧"},{"pid":"e9c85f15885b4e0d0437bc2ca73d48fd67ea7a59","tid":2022676,"uid":56498,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"做緊Marketing的shitty畢業生路過<br />\n發現有d人問嘅問題真係on99￼￼<br />\n<br />\n1. City作為一間2nd tier的學校，個朵比唔上三大是常識吧<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果有心做digital，根本唔應該讀marketing 呢D文科野，應該去讀D更加technical 的科目先係<br />\n<br />\n3. FG avg $